This is the README file for the ASAP 3 project


DIRECTORY STRUCTURE
===================

Basics:

  The source files for the central parts of Asap, including the calculators.

Brenner:

  The library for the Brenner potential.

Debug:

  Files helpful when debugging.

Examples:

  Example scripts.

Interface:

  The C++/Python interface.

Parallel:

  Source code for parallel simulations using MPI.

Python:

  The Python modules.

Test:

  The test suite.

Swig:

  Leftovers from Asap 2, soon to go away.


